S - bakers chocolate and coffee. the slightest hint of the chili peppers in the background
T - Coffee to start, transitioning to the chili's and then to deep, dark chocolate... a slight heat on the back end from the chili's - not overpowering, but somehow pulls the whole thing together very nicely. Alcohol is not noticeable at all.
